<strong>Resistance Mechanism</strong>: Magnetic</li><li><strong>Product Weight</strong>: 53 lbs</li><li><strong>Assembly</strong>: Yes, tools and instructions included</li><li><strong>Maximum Weight Capacity</strong>: 300 lbs</li><li><strong>Best Uses For</strong>: Daily exercise</li><li><strong>Special Feature</strong>: Extra-large side handles</li><li><strong>Warranty</strong>: 2-year limited manufacturer warranty</li><li><strong>Package</strong>: Bike, user manual, instruction tools</li></ul></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675858963355" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1675858963355"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-xs gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>The <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B002KV1MJU?tag=best-exercise-bike-for-seniors-20" class="" target="_blank">Marcy ME-709</a> recumbent bike is made from 14-gauge steel tubing. It has a reliable weight capacity of up to 300 lbs. Furthermore, the frame is powder-coated to protect it against rust and basic wear and tear.</p><p>With its step-through design and low seat position, the bike offers quick and easy mounting and dismounting. This is especially beneficial for seniors or individuals with mobility issues that find climbing onto regular stationary bikes troublesome. Additionally, the bike can be rolled around using the transportation wheels on the bottom if you need to move it from place to place.</p><p>The high-density foam seat and backrest provide a comfortable workout, while the oversized, contoured, foam-covered handles on the side help users maintain balance and posture when necessary. For added convenience and safety, the textured foot pedals are counterbalanced, promoting smooth and steady pedaling. The adjustable foot straps keep your feet securely in place, preventing any slippage during intense workouts.</p><p>Th